# The "Cloud"
 
It is very hard to get clear estimates, but it appears there are on the order of a few hundred million servers making up the "cloud".  Or on the order of 10 people per server.  

 - On the order a few hundred billion dollars globally($100/person globally)
 - 1e23 bytes of information (1 Tb/person globally)

[![](https://www.cloudwards.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Cloud-Computing-Stats-By-the-Numbers.png)](https://www.cloudwards.net/cloud-computing-statistics/)

